snippet.title: Amber Heard Befittingly Responds To 'Campaign' Against Her 'Aquaman 2' Role
snippet.description:
Amber Heard kept her composure amid Johnny Depp's fans demanding her to leave Aquaman 2. The actress, in an interview, thanked her fans for always applauding her and assured the movie's release next year.
Visit: https://www.thecelebpost.com/news/7764-amber-heard-befittingly-responds-to-campaign-against-her-aquaman-2-role
